Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我來了 Mk.Nicht
